Package: AutoStat
Title: Automated Statistical Analysis Using Large Language Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Xianyang", "Zhang", 
    email = "zhangxiany@stat.tamu.edu", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Leverages large language models to automate statistical analysis tasks.
    Users provide a dataset and research question, and the package determines appropriate
    analysis methods, executes them, and produces interpretable reports.
